  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out an optimal way of analgesia in case of acute
      infectious gastroenteritis the investigators are going to compare two medicines that are used
      on everyday basis (without being ever before subject to scientifical study): Dipyrone and
      papaverine The study is done in the Emergency Department setting. Thus, only first 6 hours of
      treatment is included in study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
